Package ch.zhaw.it.pm3.spacerunner.technicalservices.visual.manager

Class VisualManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.zhaw.it.pm3.spacerunner.technicalservices.visual.manager.VisualManager
  • public class VisualManager
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a Manager for the Visuals of the different VisualElement's. It is implemented with the singleton-pattern. The Manager was implemented because for example all Asteroids share the same image. => So it would make no sense to have the image in every element itself. The image is set per Class of VisualElement (? extends VisualElement)
